snippet: In a sign a new peace deal may not hold, South Sudan's government and rebels accused each other of attacks Saturday that come after the cease-fire was supposed to take hold....

headline.print_headline: Fighting Reported in S. Sudan Despite Cease-Fire
headline.main: Fighting Reported in S. Sudan Despite Cease-Fire

lead_paragraph: In a sign a new peace deal may not hold, South Sudan's government and rebels accused each other of attacks Saturday that come after the cease-fire was supposed to take hold.
